skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tribes ascend
des:
Check easily is anybody playing Tribes Ascend right now. It will check both on official (Hi-Rez) and on community servers.

We are using Steam and Griffon's API for retrieving information so the data is accurate as much as they are.

This service is in no way associated or affiliated with Steam or Hi-Rez Studios.
